1. *Pravom* nam se obavezno vratiti novac. (We must definitely return the money.)
2. Oni su u *pravu*. (They are right.)
3. Gledamo *pravo* u oči. (We are looking each other straight in the eye.)
4. Ona je *prava* na svoj stav. (She is firm in her attitude.)
5. Kupili smo *pravu* stvar. (We bought the right thing.)
6. Oni se ponašaju *pravo*. (They are behaving properly.)
7. Ona je došla u *pravo* vreme. (She arrived at the right time.)
8. On je *pravi* čovek za posao. (He is the right man for the job.)